text: The Rocketeer is a 1991 period superhero adventure movie set in 1938 and was directed by Joe Johnston and stars Billy Campbell, Jennifer Connelly, Alan Arkin, Timothy Dalton, Paul Sorvino, and Terry O'Quinn. It was distributed by Walt Disney Pictures. == Other websites == * * * * Category:1991 movies Category:1991 adventure movies Category:American adventure movies Category:American superhero movies Category:Movies set in Los Angeles Category:Movies set in the 1930s
